@startuml
title 学生购买课程时序图

actor 学生
participant OrderController
participant OrderService
participant UserService
participant CourseService
participant EnrollmentService
participant PaymentGateway

学生 -> OrderController: 请求创建课程订单
OrderController -> OrderService: 创建课程订单
OrderService -> UserService: 验证学生账号状态
UserService --> OrderService: 返回账号状态正常
OrderService -> CourseService: 获取课程价格信息
CourseService --> OrderService: 返回课程详情
OrderService -> OrderService: 检查是否重复购买
OrderService --> OrderController: 返回订单信息
OrderController --> 学生: 显示订单确认页面

学生 -> OrderController: 确认支付订单
OrderController -> OrderService: 处理支付请求
OrderService -> PaymentGateway: 发送支付请求
PaymentGateway --> OrderService: 返回支付成功
OrderService -> OrderService: 更新订单状态为已支付
OrderService -> EnrollmentService: 开通课程学习权限
EnrollmentService --> OrderService: 确认权限已开通
OrderService --> OrderController: 返回支付成功
OrderController --> 学生: 显示购买成功，可开始学习
@enduml